snippet.title: The Mathemagician
snippet.description:
Meet Art Benjamin, the mathemagician who multiplies numbers lightening quick. He teaches you some of his techniques and performs his magic.


Twitter: @TPointMath

Images:

Numbers: Morebyless
Cards: Robert Kouse-Baker
Black and White Art Benjamin photos: Anne White
Art Benjamin with top hat: Richard Faverty

Music:

"All This" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
